/**
 * @description  here we are removing the denomination note amount from the returned amount....
 * @date
 * @method       removeReturnDenominations:
 * @author
 * @param
 * @param
 * @param
 * @param
 * @param
 * @return       void
 *
 * @modified By  Srinivasulu on 18/11/2017....
 * @reason       added the comments....
 *
 * @verified By
 * @verified On
